title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 24 2022
description:
NYC subway murderer, Andrew Abdullah, with 19 prior arrests turns himself in. ISIS terrorist caught plotting to smuggle Iraqis across border to kill George W. Bush. GA Primary Day with C&B: Governor Brian Kemp joins Clay and Buck to make his final argument. Callers with multiple arrests share their stories.
